org.jlab.mya

Class Event

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jlab.mya.Event
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Event>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    FloatEvent, IntEvent, MultiStringEvent

    public abstract class Event
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Event>
    A Mya history event such as an update or discontinuity marker. This class is abstract as concrete implementations provide values of various data types which may also be vector or scalar in nature. In practice Mya treats all vectors as collections of Strings and only allows scalar floats and ints.
    Author:
    slominskir
